English:
I got to join the team because I live in Nakano.
Maybe they'll kick me out if I move away?
Chinese:
我只是剛好住在中野而已～
就被拉去參加隊伍了啊～
要是搬家的話會願意讓我退出嗎～？
Korean:
나카노에 산다는 것만으로~
팀에 가입되어버렸네요~
이사하면 탈퇴 당하는 걸까~?
German:
Ich durfte ins Team, weil ich in Nakano wohne.
Wenn ich umziehe, schmeißen sie mich vielleicht
raus?

English: I don't know. Does that person live in Nakano?
Chinese:
不曉得～？
那個人，是住在中野嗎～？
Korean:
모르겠네요~?
그 사람, 나카노에 사는 건가요~?
German: Keine Ahnung. Wohnt diese Person in Nakano?

English: I like Nakano, but Ikebukuro's nice, too.
Chinese: 中野雖然很棒～但是池袋也很不錯呢～
German:
Ich mag Nakano, aber in Ikebukuro ist es auch
schön.
